{"tid":747142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[偽環保] 走塑？真的走到塑？","createTime":"2018-07-18T06:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T12:08:18.000Z","uid":41818,"like":251,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e7eb30ba146f286e95c3fbf2819080f829501f","tid":747142,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/37242388_482008598906190_5924332310185902080_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=49a07f1fdd0011553f03514376586de3&amp;oe=5BE67F30\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F37242388_482008598906190_5924332310185902080_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D49a07f1fdd0011553f03514376586de3%26oe%3D5BE67F30&h=3dd8c9a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n走塑的爭議<br />\n<br />\n本月較早前，在西雅圖首次強制實施在當地禁止使用塑料吸管之後，Starbucks 隨即宣布不再提供其特許經營範圍內的吸管，取而代之的是一種不使用吸管的新「吸管杯」二合一式蓋子。此舉贏得了環保團體及人士的讚揚，同時呼籲更多公司效仿。<br />\n<br />\n但事實是否成功走塑呢？根據外國媒體reason所報導，新蓋子實際上比舊蓋子和吸管兩者所使用的塑料更多。舊蓋子和吸管含有3.55克塑料。新蓋子含有4.11克塑料。<br />\n<br />\n看來「始料不及後果定律」（the law of unintended consequences）再次出現了。<br />\n<br />\n更重要的是，所有名人發言和政治立法都忽略了一個基本事實：吸管構成不了問題，當然也解決不了問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1*tApmiYToszhgxklAPoGYfA@2x.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-images-1.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1600%2F1%2AtApmiYToszhgxklAPoGYfA%402x.jpeg&h=df8b2064&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在2015年一段片段中，一隻海龜鼻子裡卡著吸管，這震撼畫面被瘋狂轉載並引起人們對海洋塑料污染問題的關注。<br />\n<br />\n但是只針對吸管的關注是完全錯誤的。據估計，每年進入海洋的900萬噸會分解成微塑料並滲入海洋生物的胃和肉中的塑料垃圾，吸管僅佔2000噸。 換句話說，無吸管活動支持者正集中精力解決塑料污染問題的0.02％。<br />\n<br />\n至於美國的廢物，也不會造成大部分的污染問題。美國擁有世界上最好的廢物處理工業之一，只有1％的塑料廢物會進入海洋。相反，造成海洋野生動物食膠的真正罪魁禍首，是那些缺乏完善的廢物回收系統及條例，較貧窮及落後的沿海國家，他們無法處理垃圾，只能到海洋傾倒。<br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，但這真相並不能提醒支持走塑的環保人士及團體所忽略了的99.98％實際問題。 因為把飲管塑造成邪惡稻草人往死裡打，更能顯示他們的環保意識，小恩小惠彷彿能讓自己心靈得到救贖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@qoloophk/%E8%B5%B0%E5%A1%91%E7%9A%84%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-c6751ca1f07c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40qoloophk%2F%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%25A1%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0-c6751ca1f07c&d=1TTr1zPgDAwmDBLIUtEFKI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b0b2a623\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@qoloophk/%E8%B5%B0%E5%A1%91%E7%9A%84%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-c6751ca1f07c</a>"},{"pid":"7d8f9af3340594cf713b3af1aeb31f33eefa23d5","tid":747142,"uid":5159,"like":223,"dislike":0,"score":223,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:58:45.000Z","msg":"小恩小惠彷彿能讓自己心靈得到救贖。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e04972d95f0a5396d8d99afd85e9355661c628","tid":747142,"uid":63870,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:00:13.000Z","msg":"捐錢比科學家研究環保物料代替塑膠會唔會實際啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e581d03a5a4ef2e25fe97ac720fbdebf4d341d","tid":747142,"uid":9115,"like":97,"dislike":2,"score":95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:01:05.000Z","msg":"所以d環保團體真係好撚on9<br />\n膠袋係一個例子,飲管又一例子"},{"pid":"2f1cbe6185fdd110603f162a79c922d02a157264","tid":747142,"uid":1221,"like":4,"dislike":48,"score":-44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/230932_7a3f48a8c346e347196fde1860027491.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F230932_7a3f48a8c346e347196fde1860027491.png&h=b6f27c8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b279d1a93b10c8bdf367b60def010ea7673c3cb6","tid":747142,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d8f9af3340594cf713b3af1aeb31f33eefa23d5","tid":747142,"uid":5159,"like":223,"dislike":0,"score":223,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:58:45.000Z","msg":"小恩小惠彷彿能讓自己心靈得到救贖。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87f6b701369cbc31898bb1e59f21eb2e4a64feb","tid":747142,"uid":8048,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"破壞更多野 保衛一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bff7b4d5a8ff9992f5cff1c3b61f923cb3a6861","tid":747142,"uid":6752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:06:38.000Z","msg":"虛偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ede8dea3764cc0b5d98cb15550e9b6c171b145","tid":747142,"uid":144899,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"環保？我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ce24878c7860a302e908d7c14fdaeb7a7bcf6e","tid":747142,"uid":104218,"like":63,"dislike":4,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"環保撚真係柒到無朋友<br />\n以為贏咗點知輸得更多"},{"pid":"828d8ef32df59f087d338d421fae8837f99ded1c","tid":747142,"uid":1327,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:13:20.000Z","msg":"其實任何事都係兩個方向<br />\n無論環保/政治 所有要人為左長期利益而甘遠放棄遠期利益<br />\n必然有兩樣野都要做得好甚至係要同步做得好先得<br />\n第一就係道德感召<br />\n第二就係實際辦法<br />\n<br />\n如果單靠道德感召而冇實際辦法 最後都會為做而做<br />\n但如果單靠實際辦法而冇道德感召 最後其實即係源頭減廢 <br />\n社會係用左好多代價先做到同一樣的野<br />\n<br />\n最慘而家個社會好似成日都搵唔到點樣平衡呢2個方向<br />\n變左受道德感召的攻擊冇的 冇的又攻擊有的<br />\n或者變左大財團VS環保組織VS小市民VS政府<br />\n永遠都唔係一行人一步"},{"pid":"ec9ebd33494b97d1e804ab921c7bba7d2078f7f7","tid":747142,"uid":104218,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2f1cbe6185fdd110603f162a79c922d02a157264","tid":747142,"uid":1221,"like":4,"dislike":48,"score":-44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/230932_7a3f48a8c346e347196fde1860027491.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F230932_7a3f48a8c346e347196fde1860027491.png&h=b6f27c8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply